TCHK1A  10                             15 13'HIT F3 TO CLOSE THE PROGRAM, MINIM-
     A                                      IZE THE AS/400 SCREEN(DO NOT'
     A                                      COLOR(PNK)
TCHK1A  10                             16 13'CLOSE) AND CLICK THE ICON FOR DOWN-
